
                        / MiniTwit /

           because writing todo lists is not fun


    ~ What is MiniTwit?

      A SQLite and Flask powered twitter clone

    ~ How do I use it?

      1. edit the configuration in the minitwit.py file or
         export an MINITWIT_SETTINGS environment variable
         pointing to a configuration file.

      2. install both the minitwitWebapp and minitwitAPI apps by running the following 
		 command from the root of each project directories

         pip install --editable .

      4. fire up a shell and run these commands to get the backend running:
		 export FLASK_APP=minitwit_api
         flask initdb
         flask run

      4. fire up another shell and run these commands to get the frontend running:
		 export FLASK_APP=minitwit
         flask run -p 5001

         the webapp will running at
         http://localhost:5001/
